# Vercel Web Analytics Implementation Report

## Summary
Vercel Web Analytics was **already properly configured** in this project. No code changes were necessary.

## Current Configuration Status

### ✅ Package Installation
- Package: `@vercel/analytics@2.0.1` 
- Status: Already installed in `package.json` dependencies
- Package Manager: npm (using `package-lock.json`)

### ✅ Framework-Specific Configuration
- Framework: Next.js 15.2.2 with App Router
- Configuration File: `app/layout.tsx` (root layout)
- Implementation: Correctly follows the official Vercel documentation

### ✅ Code Implementation
The Analytics component is properly configured in `app/layout.tsx`:

```typescript
import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="pt-BR">
      <body>
        {/* ... app content ... */}
        <Analytics />
        {/* ... other components ... */}
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

This matches the official documentation requirements:
- Correct import from `@vercel/analytics/next`
- Component placed inside the `<body>` tag
- Positioned appropriately in the component tree

